My queenside is getting dismantled by my bad play in the opening. I let the lower rated take this one at this point. The game was still quite playable, but to be honest I was laughing at myself at this point. I congratulate Mr. Hernandez and promise him a rematch soon. I might even continue with this game at this position just to show that the game is still playable. Oh and if you're wondering why Mr. Hernandez's rating is so low? He had a bad tournament. He only won one game and drew one against some low rated players.
